  ### Travailler avec plusieurs branches

  récupérer une branche distante
  ```sh
  git checkout -t origin/feature/update-reviews
  ```

  rename branch
  ```sh
  git branch -m feature/old-branch feature/new-branch
  ```

  delete branch
  ```sh
  git branch -d feature/merged-branch
  ```

